summary: This is my new house with beautiful paintings and a cozy sleep room with wonderful views to Whiterun!   Enjoy
descriptionHtml:
My flying Fortress

This is my new house with beautiful paintings and a cozy sleep room with wonderful views to Whiterun! The entrance is located directly across from breezehome. 
Enjoy

Included are:
a Forge
a Workbench
a Grindstone
a Tanning Rack
an Alchemy Table
an Enchanting Table
a Smelter
three NPCs
a small Alchemy Garden and more but see for yourself


A big thanks goes to Artisanix! Thank you for your mod resource:
Paintings and frames: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/17423
I replaced the texture of the images with others! Hope you enjoy it, have fun!


If you do not like a picture, you can delete it with this console Command: \"\" disable \"\"

Install MAIN
Drag and drop all into your Skyrim Data Folder!


Install UPDATE = added five Mannequins
Drag and drop it into your Skyrim Data Folder!
Replace it with the existing file.
author: Rakani
